title: #92Noon: Nordo in for PA! Evason/de St. Aubin/Leber/Davidson
description: Eric Nordquist is in the big chair for PA! Head Coach to the Minnesota Wild Dean Evason. Kyndra de St. Aubin talks Minnesota Loons. Marshall, Minnesota is where it's at. Ben Leber joins for some NFL draft aftermath talk. And Viking rookie TE, Zach Davidson calls in.
